---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Contact — PlayShip"
  description="Reach PlayShip by email or WhatsApp. Based in Camberley, United Kingdom."
>
  <main class="container legal">
    <p class="eyebrow mono">CONTACT</p>
    <h1>Contact</h1>
    <p class="updated mono">Replies within 12 hours, Mon–Fri GMT/BST.</p>

    <p>
      PlayShip is operated as PlayShip UK (sole trader, Avinash Sreekumar),
      based in the United Kingdom. The fastest way to start a project is the
      <a href="/#intake">intake form</a>. For anything else, use the channels
      below.
    </p>

    <h2>Email</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="mailto:avinashsreekumar007@gmail.com">avinashsreekumar007@gmail.com</a>
    </p>

    <h2>WhatsApp</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/447436393808" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">+44 7436 393808</a>
      — text first, please. Voice calls by appointment.
    </p>

    <h2>Business address</h2>
    <p>
      PlayShip UK (sole trader, Avinash Sreekumar)<br />
      Camberley, United Kingdom<br />
      Full postal address provided on invoice request.
    </p>

    <h2>Office hours</h2>
    <p>
      Monday to Friday, 09:00–18:00 UK time (GMT/BST). Closed on weekends and
      UK public holidays. Urgent rejection-recovery cases handled outside
      hours when possible.
    </p>

    <h2>What to include</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>App name and Play Store URL (if it already exists)</li>
      <li>Current status: pre-submission, in testing, rejected, or suspended</li>
      <li>Tier of interest, or "not sure"</li>
      <li>Any deadline you are working toward</li>
    </ul>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 760px;
    padding-block: 80px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--approved);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  h1 {
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  h2 {
    margin-top: 40px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .updated {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  p, li {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  li {
    margin-block: 6px;
  }
  a {
    color: var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--line-strong);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  a:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--ink);
  }
</style>
